国队只需 1 分便可锁定出线席位，因此锋线减员相对来说并没有那么致命，包括费南多和韦世豪等攻击手都能撑起防反战术，而防守端的缺兵少将才是中国队面临的最大挑战。 鉴于在李帅和高准翼因伤病退出集训后，中国队在边后卫位置上的用人已捉襟见肘，教练组决定临时征调李磊入队。李磊此前也曾遭遇伤病，但近期恢复情况不错，能够达到训练和比赛条件，很有可能在对垒韩国队一役被委以重任。 韩国队目前也在为世预赛亚洲区 36 强赛末轮比赛做准备，昨天仅吴世勋和郑又荣两将未参加场地训练，意味着「太极虎」大概率会在比赛中祭出强阵。从去年 11 月主场对垒韩国队的比赛情况来看，国足客战韩国想要守住 1 分并不容易，但在已无退路的情况下，全队必须放手一搏。 津媒：国足客战韩国想守住 1 分不容易，李磊很有可能被委以重任"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f1a872ef45eec722465ca5d6ff0ad82f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658539792"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwoTZrOmvobIREAMaCTEwODYyMDI4NCDS5JmzBjAAOIgBQC5yCTY1ODUzOTc5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1718094293.13394", "card_id": "Q_658268826", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你的高中生活快乐吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658268826"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwoTZrOmvobIREAMaCTEwODU2MDA2MCCIuYezBjAAOElAL3IJNjU4MjY4ODI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1718094293.13637", "card_id": "Q_656087059", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "户外登山有哪些必备的硬核防晒好物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-07301ec6af63b31a124997a729d643a7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656087059"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IwoTZrOmvobIR